\max \{4,5\}=d(4,5)= 1
\begin{align} \max\{4,5\} &= \frac{4-5}{2}+ \frac{4+5}{2} \\                               &= \frac{-1}{2}+\frac{1}{2}  \\ &= 0\end{align}
